, which was\nnot known before. Our approach is markedly different from prior works\nestablishing spectral independence for spin systems using spatial mixing\n\\cite{ALO20, CLV20, CGSV20, FGYZ20}, which crucially is still open in this\nregime for proper list-colorings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Mar 2021 06:32:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 17 Jul 2021 07:02:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-20"}
