 a future research agenda for leveraging\nmulti-source patent embeddings, their appropriateness across applications, as\nwell as to improve and validate patent embeddings by creating domain-expert\ncurated Semantic Textual Similarity (STS) benchmark datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Mar 2021 15:23:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 29 May 2021 15:06:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 17 Oct 2021 06:27:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-19"}
